N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1261.46 - Moving aircraft to be under control and moved at reasonable speed

State Regulations

All aircraft which are being taxied, towed or otherwise
moved at an air terminal shall be under full control and shall move or be moved
at a reasonable speed. Notes
